The Americans have a new "intelligent weapon"
The U.S. military sent a new “smart” weapon to Afghanistan, known only as the code XM-25.
The generals believe that this new automatic rifle will influence the conflict there with the Taliban and "will change the game" to their advantage.
The new weapon is like a super precise cannon
Its projectiles are laser-guided with a precision of a few meters.
The special ammunition of 25 mm caliber developed for this rifle and containing a highly breakable explosive, actually works like small grenades.
